Lilley, David G 





Professor Emeritus
Mechanical and Aerospace Engineering
	Oklahoma State University
	Engineering North 218
	Stillwater, Oklahoma 74078-5016 USAPhone: (405) 744-5900Fax: (405) 744-7873E-mail:lilley@okstate.edu

	 

	Areas of Interest

		Combustion

		Heat Transfer

		Computational Fluid Dynamics

		Fire Dynamics

		Fuels, Flammability, Fires and Flames

		Fire Investigation Technical Aspects

		Technical Aspects of Explosions

		Computer Graphics and Animation

		Combustion, Aerodynamics, Fires, Fuels, Sprays, Heat Transfer and Fluid Dynamics

		Software Development in Fluid Dynamics, Heat Transfer, and Combustion

